          "id": "medmcqa-defafb75-e1d8-454c-84fe-a326151e3cba",
          "text": "Shailza, a 40-year-old female is having headache for the past 6 months. All her investigations were normal. She had several consultations and she had no relief of her symptoms. She still believes that she has some problem in her brain. Likely diagnosis could be: September 2010",
