          "id": "medmcqa-c98a8cfb-ba5d-4cb8-ade4-0e0448d72ea8",
          "text": "20 years old female with complaints of nausea, vomiting, dizziness and pain in the legs. Her physical examination and all lab investigations and radiological investigations are normal. What would be the most probable diagnosis?",
