          "explanation": "Suicide is a psychiatric emergency. Suicide is preventable and can be identified early using a scale called as SAD PERSONS scale. Other impoant psychiatric emergencies are neuroleptic malignant syndrome Serotonin syndrome Agitated patient Ref.Kaplon and sadock, synopsis of psychiatry, 11 th edition, pg no. 763",
