          "text": "A man came with his wife in the psychiatric depament. She is complaining about his increased cleanliness. He keeps on washing hands in frequent intervals telling that it's not clean. He wants everything in an ordered manner. He is becoming obsessive in everything and compelling everyone at home to follow him. Which of the following drug is most useful in this patient?",
