          "id": "medmcqa-e162d7cf-4319-4bdd-a6ae-4e27a7085717",
          "text": "A 29 year old woman has severe manic episode. She has been diagnosed with bipolar affective disorder. Among the following, which one is not used for the prophylaxis of her illness?",
