          "correctOptionId": "opt-2",
          "explanation": "Adverse Effects of ECT A. Memory disturbances: it is the most common side effect of ECT. Both retrograde andanterograde amnesia is seen.retrograde amnesia is much more common.B. Headache, muscle aches, fractures (very rare with modifiedECT), nausea and vomiting.",
