          "id": "medmcqa-dd049663-f245-4459-87ae-aa64efb9e860",
          "text": "A patient with pneumonia for 5 days is admitted to the hospital in altered sensorium. He suddenly ceases to recognize the doctor and staff. He thinks that he is in jail and complains of scorpion attacking him. His probable diagnosis is:",
