          "id": "medmcqa-272e6025-8de2-4dc5-b1d2-8f43ac09115b",
          "text": "A person of 35 years is having a firm belief about infidelity involving the spouse. And he never allows her to go out of home alone. He often locks his house, while going office. Despite all this, he is persistently suspicious about her character. The probable diagnosis is-",
