          "id": "medmcqa-977742e4-f01c-4324-a6a4-6e49a3990851",
          "text": "25 yr old gentleman has repeated thoughts that he has not locked his car door properly, frequently checks it while driving, he repeatedly checks locks in his house. Diagnosis",
