          "id": "medmcqa-44089053-e052-49d6-abde-58cc2b389bee",
          "text": "A 70-year-old man presents with h/o prosopagnosia, loss of memory, 3rd person hallucinations since 1 month. On examination deep tendon reflexes are increased, mini-mental examination score is 20/30. What is most likely diagnosis?",
