          "explanation": "D i.e. Patchy impairment of personal memories Psychogenic (Dissociative) amnesia is commonest clinical type of dissociative disorder. It is characterized by a sudden inability to recall impoant personal information paicularly concerning stressful or traumatic life events.Q"
