          "id": "medmcqa-5358cc5c-64d2-4f7f-8fa4-266a5170a85d",
          "text": "A 9 yr old child is found to be restless. He is hyperactive and his teacher complains that he does not listen to teaching in the class, disturbs other students and also shows less interest in playing. The likely diagnosis is:",
