          "id": "medmcqa-eb257af1-e9e3-4e64-805d-9b1cc8ed0bab",
          "text": "A 60 year old male comes to casuality with acute retention of urine since 12 hours. On examination there was distended bladder. His son gives a history of taking some drug by the pateint. Since 2 days as he is suffering from depression. The most likely drug is",
